		<title>Banned Questions About Jesus – Christian Piatt, Ed. [Review]</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/EnglewoodRadioBiblio/~3/rbEJoLAIMXo/</link>
		<comments>http://erb.kingdomnow.org/banned-questions-about-jesus-christian-piatt-ed-review/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Tue, 05 Jun 2012 20:59:23 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>EnglewoodReview@gmail.com (THE ENGLEWOOD REVIEW OF BOOKS)</dc:creator>
